	<title>Report Templates Preview View</title>

	<section>
		<para>
			You can easily preview report templates, set different zoom levels, and print a template. To open the Report Templates Preview view,
			select
			<menuchoice>
				<guimenu>Window</guimenu>
				<guimenuitem>Show View</guimenuitem>
				<guimenuitem>Other...</guimenuitem>
				<guimenuitem>Jaspersoft Studio</guimenuitem>
				<guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem>
			</menuchoice>
			, then select a report template, a file of type
			<filename class='extension'>.jrxml</filename>
			or
			<filename class='extension'>.jasper</filename>
			.
		</para>

		<figure>
			<title>Preview Report Templates View</title>
			<screenshot>
				<mediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="preview_templates.png" format="PNG" />
					</imageobject>
				</mediaobject>
			</screenshot>
		</figure>
	</section>

</section>